cc.mallet.fst.confidence

Interface TransducerCorrector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConstrainedViterbiTransducerCorrector, IsolatedSegmentTransducerCorrector

    public interface TransducerCorrector
    Interface for transducerCorrectors, which correct a subset of the Segments produced by a Transducer. It's primary purpose is to find the Segments that the Transducer is least confident in and correct those using the true Labeling (correctLeastConfidenceSegments).
